## ğŸ—‚ï¸ Dataset

- **Dataset:** [CIFAR-10](https://www.cs.toronto.edu/~kriz/cifar.html)
- Automatically loaded using `tensorflow.keras.datasets.cifar10`.

Each image is **32x32 pixels** and belongs to one of 10 classes:
airplane, automobile, bird, cat, deer, dog, frog, horse, ship, truck

Input (32x32x3)
â”‚
â”œâ”€â”€ Conv2D (32 filters, 3x3) + ReLU + MaxPooling
â”œâ”€â”€ Conv2D (64 filters, 3x3) + ReLU + MaxPooling
â”œâ”€â”€ Conv2D (128 filters, 3x3) + ReLU + MaxPooling
â”œâ”€â”€ Flatten
